#: ../../modules/core/core_model.rst:182
msgid "Solving a Model Classically"
msgstr "Resoldre un model de manera clàssica"

#: ../../modules/core/core_model.rst:184
msgid ""
"To help demonstrate the limits of classical solvers, a variety of "
"wrappers to different solvers are provided:"
msgstr ""
"Per ajudar a demostrar els límits dels resolutors clàssics, es "
"proporcionen diversos embolcalls per a diferents resolutors:"

#: ../../modules/core/core_model.rst:186
msgid ""
":class:`~qilisdk.utils.classical_solvers.brute_force_solver.BruteForceSolver`"
" - A brute-force solver that evaluates all possible solutions."
msgstr ""
":class:`~qilisdk.utils.classical_solvers.brute_force_solver.BruteForceSolver`"
" - Un resolutor de força bruta que avalua totes les solucions possibles."

#: ../../modules/core/core_model.rst:187
msgid ""
":class:`~qilisdk.utils.classical_solvers.scipy_solver.ScipySolver` - A "
"solver that uses one of SciPy's `optimize` routines to find a solution."
msgstr ""
":class:`~qilisdk.utils.classical_solvers.scipy_solver.ScipySolver` - Un "
"resolutor que utilitza una de les rutines `optimize` de SciPy per trobar "
"una solució."

#: ../../modules/core/core_model.rst:188
msgid ""
":class:`~qilisdk.utils.classical_solvers.scip_solver.ScipSolver` - A "
"wrapper to SCIP, a mixed-integer programming solver. This requires the "
"SCIP extra (i.e. `pip install qilisdk[scip]`)."
msgstr ""
":class:`~qilisdk.utils.classical_solvers.scip_solver.ScipSolver` - Un "
"embolcall per a SCIP, un resolutor de programació entera mixta. Això "
"requereix l'extra de SCIP (és a dir, `pip install qilisdk[scip]`)."

